{"tid":2328992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中文維基提出禁止收錄媒體主播及記者名單","createTime":"2020-12-17T02:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T17:13:16.000Z","uid":10540,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4439d7ab2bc4808ce75267ca393bf9a577c0e684","tid":2328992,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T02:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EyfzKth.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEyfzKth.jpg&h=be3c4d37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自有線新聞裁員事件發生後，來自香港的維基百科用戶以「瑣碎，原始研究及愛好者內容」為由，刪除now新聞同無線新聞的成員名單，包括媒體主播及記者資料過往在電視台的職位及現時的去向，亦包括已經去世的人員，而有關名單已經存在15年，並有參考價值。<br />\n<br />\n有關的舉動對大量媒體條目的影響非常大（主要以香港和台灣為主），嚴重影響讀者了解媒體公司和人物的背景，亦無法得知過往的歷史。其後雖然有用戶重新記載，也被相關的用戶定為「破壞」條目為由而被封禁。<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">而提刪的用戶更提出在方針建立條文，禁止新聞媒體條目內嵌入現職和離職的記者及員工列表。</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A9%E5%AE%A2%E6%A0%88/%E6%96%B9%E9%92%88#%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E6%A2%9D%E7%9B%AE%E5%85%A7%E5%B5%8C%E5%85%A5%E7%8F%BE%E8%81%B7%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8A%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWikipedia%3A%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25A0%2588%2F%25E6%2596%25B9%25E9%2592%2588%23%25E7%25A6%2581%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%25A2%259D%25E7%259B%25AE%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25B5%258C%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%2581%25B7%25E5%2592%258C%25E9%259B%25A2%25E8%2581%25B7%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%258F%258A%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE16crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=3938f186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A9%E5%AE%A2%E6%A0%88/%E6%96%B9%E9%92%88#%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E6%A2%9D%E7%9B%AE%E5%85%A7%E5%B5%8C%E5%85%A5%E7%8F%BE%E8%81%B7%E5%92%8C%E9%9B%A2%E8%81%B7%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%8F%8A%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A9%E5%AE%A2%E6%A0%88/%E6%9D%A1%E7%9B%AE%E6%8E%A2%E8%AE%A8#%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E6%87%89%E5%90%A6%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FWikipedia%3A%25E4%25BA%2592%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E6%25A0%2588%2F%25E6%259D%25A1%25E7%259B%25AE%25E6%258E%25A2%25E8%25AE%25A8%23%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A7%258B%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE16crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=afac1971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A9%E5%AE%A2%E6%A0%88/%E6%9D%A1%E7%9B%AE%E6%8E%A2%E8%AE%A8#%E7%A4%BE%E7%BE%A4%E6%87%89%E5%90%A6%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E6%A9%9F%E6%A7%8B%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">事件反映目前的中文維基百科與民政署一樣，不斷利用維基設立的方針規則「搬龍門」和收緊用戶的知情權和編者的空間。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>需要大家以讀者的身份，要求保留之前記錄的媒體主播及記者名單</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\">無綫新聞 CCTVB</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Talk:%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FTalk%3A%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E&d=c